      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 🔥 KILLER PLAY\n\nThe **Nigerian WHT** cluster is the highest-leverage page on the entire site.\n\n- Search competition: essentially zero\n- Search intent: brutally commercial\n- FinMark.ai has a real, defensible differentiator\n- Expected outcome: **top 5 ranking within 4-8 weeks of indexing**\n\nIf only one page on the site ever ranks, this should be the one.",
