      "text": "## Legend\n\n🔴 **Red** — Homepage + the killer Nigerian WHT cluster\n🔵 **Cyan** — AP Pillar (the only pillar)\n🟣 **Purple** — Standard cluster pages (9)\n🟡 **Yellow** — Strategy / planning notes\n\n**Real product, not generic copy:**\n- Microsoft Dynamics NAV (not NetSuite/QuickBooks)\n- Nigerian WHT (not US sales tax)\n- Claude Opus 4.6 (not generic AI)\n- TGI Group as live customer\n- Built for African enterprise",
